We never told you.

38:10.880 --> 38:12.920
It was a terrible tragedy, Cole.

38:15.120 --> 38:17.760
I got out of the hospital late

38:18.440 --> 38:20.560
and looked after you two.

38:22.320 --> 38:24.000
But neither of you was breathing.

38:25.680 --> 38:27.920
It was a carbon monoxide leak.

38:28.240 --> 38:29.280
Dad, this is not the time...

38:29.400 --> 38:30.760
But.  Listen to me.

38:32.720 --> 38:34.640
I got you both and
your mother out.

38:34.840 --> 38:36.640
I ventilated you first.

38:38.240 --> 38:39.520
And you finally woke up

38:40.840 --> 38:44.000
but when I reached for Lola...

38:46.800 --> 38:48.400
