her, I really wanted to

38:53.400 --> 38:54.680
but it was too late.

38:54.840 --> 38:56.880
No, Cole, listen to me.

38:57.520 --> 39:00.680
Your mother loved you,
my son.  She loved you

39:01.800 --> 39:05.200
