the loss of your sister.

39:06.040 --> 39:07.040
You...

39:10.880 --> 39:13.840
No no.

39:14.960 --> 39:16.680
No, that wasn't the whole truth.

39:17.560 --> 39:19.760
We were lucky.
We were able to save one.

39:21.840 --> 39:24.080
I was overwhelmed by
the grief for the other child.

39:25.160 --> 39:26.680
It was me, Cole.

39:29.560 --> 39:32.360
I couldn't cope with the loss.

39:35.000 --> 39:37.760
Your mother was
doing badly, I knew that

39:38.040 --> 39:39.400
