39:42.720 --> 39:44.840
Because I didn't know
how to help myself.

39:47.520 --> 39:51.040
I am so sorry my son.
I am so sorry.

39:51.160 --> 39:53.800
I love you more
than anything, but...

39:54.960 --> 39:56.280
...I have disappointed you.

39:56.880 --> 39:58.080
I have disappointed you.

39:58.200 --> 40:00.760
No, you didn't let me down, dad.

40:01.880 --> 40:02.920
You didn't let me down.

40:06.360 --> 40:07.440
It's OK.

40:12.000 --> 40:13.120
I love you too.

40:14.200 --> 40:15.600
And I am here now.

